PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?language ?languageLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q225 wdt:P37 ?language .
  ?language rdfs:label ?languageLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?languageLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?senator ?senatorLabel WHERE {
  ?senator p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q4416090 ; pq:P768 ?seat .
  FILTER ( ?seat IN ( wd:Q101498883 , wd:Q101498993 ) ) ?senator rdfs:label ?senatorLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?senatorLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?givenNameLabel ?familyNameLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q312581 wdt:P735 ?givenName .
  wd:Q312581 wdt:P734 ?familyName .
  ?givenName rdfs:label ?givenNameLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?givenNameLabel ) = "en" ) .
  ?familyName rdfs:label ?familyNameLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?familyNameLabel ) = "en" ) .
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?coach ?coachLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startDate .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?endDate .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?startDate ) <= 2013 && YEAR( ?endDate ) >= 2013 ) OPTIONAL {
    ?coach rdfs:label ?coachLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?coachLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?occupation ?occupationLabel ?label ?description WHERE {
  wd:Q9200 wdt:P106 ?occupation .
  ?occupation rdfs:label ?occupationLabel .
  wd:Q9200 rdfs:label ?label .
  wd:Q9200 schema:description ?description .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?occupationLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = "en" ) FILTER ( LANG( ?description ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?superbowl ?year WHERE {
  ?superbowl wdt:P31 wd:Q32096 ; wdt:P1346 wd:Q276539 ; wdt:P585 ?date .
  BIND( YEAR( ?date ) AS ?year )
}
ORDER BY ?year

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?vicePresident ?vicePresidentLabel WHERE {
  ?vicePresident p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11699 ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "1963-11-22T23:59:59Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end >= "1961-01-20T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?vicePresident rdfs:label ?vicePresidentLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?vicePresidentLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
LIMIT 10
